Package org.anchoranalysis.experiment.log

Helpful classes for logging.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StatefulMessageLogger
    A MessageLogger that can be started and stopped, and is aware this state.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsoleMessageLogger  
    Divider
    Creates a line of text that span a certain width with a repeated character, optionally containing a label.
    FailureOnlyMessageLogger
    Writes text to a file, but only if FailureOnlyMessageLogger.close(boolean, boolean) is called with successful==true.
    MessageLoggerList  
    TextFileMessageLogger
    Logs messages to a text-file.
